column5: Does anyone have the last chip they made for Lowrance for Lake of the Woods? Does it get North of Nester Falls? thanks
It works in Morson. By "North of Nestor Falls" do you mean Sioux Narrows/Kenora? Or actually in the Nestor area?
In the Nestor area. We are renting a houseboat there. thanks

It does not cover the northern 25% of the lake. They use to put the Canadian map in its placebut now they no longer include it. It is just the lake outline.See the pdf for coveragehttp://www.cabelas.com/assets/produc...y_lakelist.pdf
check out the navionics premium Canada chip
That's what I have and it works pretty dang good.
